OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774541484
OL,3,CMan who talked down hospital bomber on
OL,4,Cvape break 'was just meant to be there'
OL,6,FA man who talked down a would be
OL,7,Fterrorist from bombing a hospital in
OL,8,FLeeds after a chance encounter outside
OL,9,Fsaid he was "just meant to be there".
OL,11,FNathan Newby was vaping outside St
OL,12,FJames's Hospital on the night of 20
OL,13,FJanuary 2023 when he came across self-
OL,14,Fradicalised extremist Mohammad Farooq.
OL,16,FFarooq, now aged 30, was carrying a
OL,17,Fpressure cooker adapted as an
OL,18,Fexplosive and planned to massacre
OL,19,Fhospital staff.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774541484
OL,3,CMan who talked down hospital bomber on
OL,4,Cvape break 'was just meant to be there'
OL,6,FBut he was convinced to hand himself
OL,7,Fin after Mr Newby engaged him in
OL,8,Fconversation for two hours.
OL,10,FMr Newby has now been awarded
OL,11,FBritain's second highest bravery
OL,12,Faward, the George Cross.
OL,14,FHe told ITV Calendar the gravity of
OL,15,Fhis intervention had "not sunk in".
OL,17,F"I was meant to be there at that time,
OL,18,Fhaving that vape, for me to bump into
OL,19,Fhim," Mr Newby said. "To talk him
OL,20,Fdown."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774541484
OL,3,CMan who talked down hospital bomber on
OL,4,Cvape break 'was just meant to be there'
OL,6,FFarooq was jailed for life with a
OL,7,Fminimum term of 37 years last year,
OL,8,Fwhen the judge Mrs Justice Cheema-
OL,9,FGrubb hailed Mr Newby's negotiating
OL,10,Fefforts as "the most remarkable" she
OL,11,Fhad ever heard.
OL,13,FMr Newby said Farooq had told him he
OL,14,Fhad recently lost his job as a nurse -
OL,15,Fafter moving jobs during the pandemic
OL,16,F- before eventually revealing he had a
OL,17,Fbomb in his bag.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774541484
OL,3,CMan who talked down hospital bomber on
OL,4,Cvape break 'was just meant to be there'
OL,6,FHe said: "When he told me the radius
OL,7,Fof what he had in the bag, I
OL,8,Fcalculated and thought 'let's get him
OL,9,Faway' because if it does go off, he'll
OL,10,Ftake the front of the building out,
OL,11,Fhe'll probably take the glass sliding
OL,12,Fdoors out - he'll do less damage.
OL,14,F"He told me he had family and kids and
OL,15,FI told him 'you're in a better place
OL,16,Fthan me because I want kids and a
OL,17,Ffamily, but I can't because of my
OL,18,Fhealth'.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774541484
OL,3,CMan who talked down hospital bomber on
OL,4,Cvape break 'was just meant to be there'
OL,6,F"It was trying to make him feel like
OL,7,Fhe was better than me. But in a way,
OL,8,Fit helped because he followed me over
OL,9,Fto the bench."
OL,11,FThe two spoke for two hours before
OL,12,Farmed officers arrived, during which
OL,13,Ftime Farooq had even "asked for a hug".
OL,15,FThe assailant had also pointed a gun
OL,16,Fat Mr Newby while he was on the phone
OL,17,Fto police, before trying to hand it
OL,18,Fover.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774541484
OL,3,CMan who talked down hospital bomber on
OL,4,Cvape break 'was just meant to be there'
OL,6,FA court later heard Farooq, bitter at
OL,7,F"perceived bullying" and fuelled by
OL,8,FIslamist extremism, had initially
OL,9,Fplanned to cause an evacuation at the
OL,10,Fhospital and lure people outside
OL,11,Fbefore setting off the bomb.
OL,13,FThe official citation for Mr Newby's
OL,14,Fmedal says "his actions in the face of
OL,15,Fimminent danger over a sustained
OL,16,Fperiod likely prevented a potentially
OL,17,Fcatastrophic event at the hospital,
OL,18,Fand ultimately saved many lives".
OL,20,FAnalysis from ITV News Calendar
OL,21,Fpresenter Lara Rostron
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
